import React, { useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import api from "../Backendroutes"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; function AddPatient() { const [form, setForm] = useState({ isOldPatient: false, docType: "OPD Registration", opdNo: "", date: "", time: "", casualty: "No", patientName: "", guardianName: "", houseNo: "", street: "", village: "", district: "", gender: "", maritalStatus: "", aadharNo: "", bloodGroup: "", mobile: "", email: "", dob: "", age: "", }); const [generatedUhid, setGeneratedUhid] = useState(""); const handleChange = (e) => { setForm({ ...form, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; // Auto calculate age const handleDobChange = (e) => { const dob = e.target.value; const birthDate = new Date(dob); const today = new Date(); console.log(today,"today") console.log(today.getFullYear(),"today getfull year") console.log(birthDate,"birthda") console.log(birthDate.getMonth(),"birthda") let age = today.getFullYear() - birthDate.getFullYear(); const m = today.getMonth() - birthDate.getMonth(); if (m < 0 || (m === 0 && today.getDate() < birthDate.getDate())) { age--; } setForm({ ...form, dob, age }); }; const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { const res = await axios.post(api.addpatient.url, form); if (res.data.success) { toast.success("Patient Registered Successfully"); setGeneratedUhid(res.data.body.uhidNo); // Reset form setForm({ isOldPatient: false, docType: "OPD Registration", opdNo: "", date: "", time: "", casualty: "No", patientName: "", guardianName: "", houseNo: "", street: "", village: "", district: "", gender: "", maritalStatus: "", aadharNo: "", bloodGroup: "", mobile: "", email: "", dob: "", age: "", }); } else { toast.error("Something went wrong"); } } catch (error) { console.log(error); toast.error("Server error"); } }; return (
